    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you say my sacrifices mattered but it doesn't feel like it. it just feels like i wasted years of my life for a result that was always gonna be the same. i have nothing left. no energy, no purpose, nothing. sometimes i just look at my bed and think how nice it would be to just... sleep and never have to wake up to this mess again. like just let it all be over.",
